full_text: I'm loving Death Note! Ha ha! It's so cheesy at times, but I'm very invested in it! Every episode I'm thinking about how the killer and detective are gonna one up each other! I love it!

That cute Subway girl gave me a free sandwich! AGAIN! Ha ha ha. It's funny. When I first met her she seemed angry, but I was like, "Damn. She cute AF! I'm gonna get to know her!". https://t.co/xKaWS5Cmu5
